longBusinessSummary: GPO Plus, Inc. organizes, promotes, and operates industry-specific group purchase organizations in the United States. It operates as a group purchasing organization for the healthcare and hemp industries, as well as offers professional services. The company is headquartered in Las Vegas, Nevada.
